revision.text:
*{{c|int '''flags'''}}
{{: BaseStatusBar SCREEN flags}}
{{: BaseStatusBar ITEM flags}}
*{{c|double '''alpha'''}}
:Determines the translucency of the image in the 0.0-1.0 range.
*{{c|vector2 '''box'''}}
:Determines the size of the box the image will be drawn in. If the size is smaller than the image, the image will be scaled to the size. The default value of {{c|(-1, -1)}} doesn't apply any box.
*{{c|vector2 '''scale'''}}
:Determines the scale of the image.
*{{c|ERenderStyle '''style'''}}
:The renderstyle of the image. Uses the same values as the {{property|RenderStyle}} property. The default value is {{c|STYLE_Translucent}}.
*{{c|color '''col'''}}
:Allows tinting the image to a specific color. The default value is FFFFFF (white), which applies no tint. The darker the color, the more visible the tint will be.
*{{c|int '''translation'''}}
:Allows applying a translation to the image. The translation can be picked from an actor pointer with <code><actorpointer>.translation</code>, or with <code>Translation.GetID('MyTranslationName')</code> where 'MyTranslationName' is a definition from the [[TRNSLATE]] lump.
*{{c|double '''clipwidth'''}}
:Allows specifying a distance in pixels beyond which the image will be clipped horizontally. {{verification}}<noinclude>[[Category:Include templates]]</noinclude>
